  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>新智元</span> <span>2025-10-20 19:32</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p>或由80万块英伟达GB300组成，算力高达16 ZettaFLOPS</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f2dcff85&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2kqAK5pLYDicAH9tq7UJtK7nw6EqDLboB1qLfNCDBJEoErQLk4QHxRJ9CFVdyrWePhq6k2zefPHmA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505152607\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb2kqAK5pLYDicAH9tq7UJtK7f3txb7greFnNibmwaqYbjkRz6EXWSbmcP7JibGRzk7DIBzFDJuxT3l8Q/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3a06df5f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2kqAK5pLYDicAH9tq7UJtK7f3txb7greFnNibmwaqYbjkRz6EXWSbmcP7JibGRzk7DIBzFDJuxT3l8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;background-color: rgb(127, 127, 127);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;background-color: rgb(127, 127, 127);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：艾伦</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;padding: 10px;font-size: 14px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;border-radius: 3px;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;word-break: break-all !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">甲骨文于上周发布全球最大云端AI超级计算机「OCI Zettascale10」，由80万块NVIDIA GPU组成，峰值算力高达16 ZettaFLOPS，成为OpenAI「星际之门」集群的算力核心。其独创Acceleron RoCE网络实现GPU间高效互联，显著提升性能与能效。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">该系统象征甲骨文在AI基础设施竞争中的强势布局。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">甲骨文在2025年AI World大会上发布OCI Zettascale10超级集群。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在拉斯维加斯举办的AI World 2025大会上，甲骨文高调推出了一台号称全球最大规模的云端AI超级计算机——OCI Zettascale10。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505152562\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.492600422832981\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2365\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2365\" data-height=\"1165\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"277\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fce52f3d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2kqAK5pLYDicAH9tq7UJtK7urmcLMePvq47pDvg3r48ibdYpPUY1BII7IGLGm8Yw84cVYib4gzycocw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgymuk12h7\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mgymv10n18xf\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个庞然大物横跨多个数据中心，由多达80万块NVIDIA GPU芯片构成，峰值计算性能被宣称可达惊人的16 ZettaFLOPS（即每秒10</span></span><sup style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\" leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mgymv10e1rg6\"><span leaf=\"\">21</span></sup></span><span data-meta-block-props=\"{&quot;blockId&quot;:&quot;7ca042b2-1330-4c7e-899b-1ab6aa6a7947&quot;,&quot;blockType&quot;:&quot;EQUATION_BLOCK&quot;,&quot;initData&quot;:{},&quot;props&quot;:{&quot;data&quot;:{&quot;equation&quot;:&quot;10^{21}\\n&quot;},&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;viewType&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;}}\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">次以上浮点运算）。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如此天文数字意味着平均每块GPU可贡献约20 PetaFLOPS算力，接近英伟达最新一代Grace Hopper（Blackwell架构GB300）芯片的水平。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">甲骨文此举无疑是在急速升温的AI算力军备竞赛中放出「大招」，试图在云端AI基础设施版图上占据一席之地。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI巨型集群的动力之源</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这套Zettascale10系统已经成为OpenAI庞大算力需求的幕后功臣。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据悉，甲骨文与OpenAI在德州阿比林（Abilene）共建了「星际之门」旗舰AI超级计算集群，而OCI Zettascale10正是其算力骨干。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505152561\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f0b82e34&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2kqAK5pLYDicAH9tq7UJtK7yjOKVz21TkHTnTusHJsMrtuFsIpbiaOAwaa7a2kASz5Ur27Suic96Srw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OpenAI基础设施部门副总裁Peter Hoeschele表示，甲骨文定制的RoCE高速网络架构在「千兆瓦级」规模下最大化了整体性能，同时将大部分能耗都用在了计算上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">换言之，甲骨文研发的这套RDMA over Converged Ethernet网络（代号Acceleron）将海量GPU紧密连接成一个整体，使得OpenAI的大模型训练能够在如此庞大的芯片阵列上高效运转。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">正因有了与OpenAI的深度合作背书，Zettascale10一亮相便自带「实战」光环，它已经在为当今业界最严苛的一些AI工作负载提供动力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Acceleron网络架构揭秘</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如此规模的GPU「巨阵」要高效运转，奥秘就在于甲骨文独创的Acceleron RoCE网络架构。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">简单来说，Acceleron让每块GPU的网络接口卡（NIC）都充当一个小型交换机，一次可连接到多个隔离的网络交换平面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种多平面、扁平化的网络设计大幅降低了GPU之间的通信延迟，并确保即使某一路由出现故障时，训练作业也能自动切换到其它路径继续运行，不至于被迫中断。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比传统三级交换结构，Acceleron减少了网络层级，使GPU对GPU的直连延迟更加一致，整体性能更具可预测性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，该架构引入了线性可插拔光学模块（LPO）和线性接收光学组件（LRO）等新技术，在不降低400G/800G带宽的前提下削减了网络的能耗与冷却成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">甲骨文称这种创新网络既提高了效率又降低了成本，让客户可以用更少的电力完成同样的AI训练任务；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">NVIDIA公司高管Ian Buck也认可道，正是这种全栈优化的「计算结构」（compute fabric）提供了将AI从实验推进到工业化所需的基础。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">峰值神话与现实考验</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">甲骨文计划在2026年下半年正式向客户提供Zettascale10集群服务，目前这一系统已开始接受预订。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而，对于16 ZFLOPS的惊人算力，不少业内观察者持保留态度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">该数据尚未经独立机构验证，而且很可能是基于理论峰值算力而非持续实效得出。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">据业内报道，甲骨文宣称的16 ZFLOPS有可能利用了极低精度的AI计算指标（例如FP8甚至4比特稀疏运算）来实现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实际的大模型训练通常需要使用更高精度（如BF16或FP8）的数值格式以保证模型收敛效果，因此16 ZFLOPS这个数字更多体现了甲骨文硬件在理想情况下的上限潜力，而非日常工作负载下可持续交付的性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 48px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这台「云端巨无霸」真正的实战表现还有待时间检验，只有等到系统明年投入使用，各种基准测试与用户实际反馈才能揭晓它能否如宣称般高效且可靠。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">云端AI竞赛的挑战与展望</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">甲骨文并非孤军奋战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当前，微软、谷歌、亚马逊等云计算巨头也在争相构建各自的大规模AI集群，它们或采购海量GPU，或研发自家AI加速硬件，云端AI算力版图正迅速扩张。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">甲骨文此次押下重注推出Zettascale10，一方面巩固了与OpenAI的战略联盟，另一方面也是向业界宣示其在AI时代不容忽视的新实力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然而在市场前景上，甲骨文依然面临如何吸引客户的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为此，该公司还发布了新的「多云通用积分」计划，允许运营商用统一的预付积分在甲骨文云及AWS、Azure、Google等多家云服务间自由调配甲骨文数据库和OCI服务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505152563\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5948051948051948\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"770\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"770\" data-height=\"458\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"334\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=76b02279&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2kqAK5pLYDicAH9tq7UJtK71qaRRic5bP8xc0S5nDUSgk1icgJBMNUicooA5U6cCswvlSVCRmpuWEP3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这项举措旨在降低客户迁移门槛、提高平台黏性，为甲骨文云生态争取更大的用户基础。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">OCI Zettascale10的出现展示了云服务商为满足AI空前算力需求所做的大胆探索。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">等到明年这套系统真正落地，我们才能知道甲骨文能否凭借这一云端「巨无霸」在激烈的AI基础设施竞赛中抢得先机，并兑现其关于高效、规模和可靠性的承诺。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/news/announcement/ai-world-oracle-unveils-next-generation-oci-zettascale10-cluster-for-ai-2025-10-14/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.oracle.com/news/announcement/ai-world-oracle-unveils-next-generation-oci-zettascale10-cluster-for-ai-2025-10-14/</a></span></span><span style=\"text-align: center;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505133683\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"122\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f15ce8a2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1y6B5OM79TFzpkceWtUkI6LEwv0uYicSoM5Q3I3kDNJhxWdL3tQvbOpU3Ty7icBqnDDNd4CCu4ibiaHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505123771\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6138888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"355\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d635e771&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYSSrl5MkKQnew6tJZbEl11vWoXJSl8KN49xb9tqpzib1NficyeTibm3pzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"2652636565\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=b2dde714&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI3MTA0MTk1MA%3D%3D%26mid%3D2652636565%26idx%3D2%26sn%3D851e63af5502eaaf25980185ea1d6032\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "甲骨文推出全球最大 AI 超算 OCI Zettascale10，搭载 80 万块英伟达 GPU，峰值算力达 16 ZFLOPS，作为 OpenAI 「星际之门」算力核心。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "甲骨文推出全球最大 AI 超算 OCI Zettascale10，搭载 80 万块英伟达 GPU，峰值算力达 16 ZFLOPS，作为 OpenAI 「星际之门」算力核心。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了甲骨文在 2025 年 AI World 大会上发布的云端 AI 超级计算机 OCI Zettascale10。该系统由多达 80 万块 NVIDIA GPU 组成，宣称峰值算力高达 16 ZettaFLOPS，旨在满足 AI 大模型训练的巨大需求。OCI Zettascale10 已成为 OpenAI 在德州阿比林共建的「星际之门」集群的算力骨干，为业界最严苛的 AI 工作负载提供动力。其核心技术亮点在于甲骨文独创的 Acceleron RoCE 网络架构，通过多平面、扁平化设计显著降低 GPU 间通信延迟，提高系统容错性，并优化能耗与冷却成本。文章也指出，16 ZFLOPS 的算力数据可能基于理论峰值或低精度计算，其实际性能和可持续交付能力仍待市场检验。甲骨文计划在 2026 年下半年正式向客户提供该集群服务，并推出「多云通用积分」计划以吸引更多客户，巩固其在云端 AI 基础设施领域的地位。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "甲骨文推出全球最大云端 AI 超算 OCI Zettascale10，峰值算力达 16 ZFLOPS。",
      "explanation": "该系统由 80 万块英伟达 GPU 组成，旨在满足 AI 大模型训练的巨大算力需求，并在云端 AI 基础设施竞争中占据关键地位。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OCI Zettascale10 作为 OpenAI 「星际之门」集群的算力骨干已投入使用。",
      "explanation": "这表明甲骨文与 OpenAI 深度合作，其超算系统已为业界最严苛的 AI 工作负载提供动力，具备实战验证。"
    },
    {
      "point": "甲骨文独创的 Acceleron RoCE 网络架构是实现大规模 GPU 高效互联的关键。",
      "explanation": "该网络通过多平面扁平化设计，显著降低 GPU 间通信延迟，提高容错性，并削减能耗与冷却成本，提升整体效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "16 ZFLOPS 峰值算力数据可能基于理论值或低精度计算，实际应用需考量。",
      "explanation": "业内观察者对此数据持保留态度，认为其可能基于极低精度计算，且尚未经独立机构验证。实际大模型训练通常需更高精度，因此 16 ZFLOPS 更多体现了硬件理想上限，而非日常工作负载下可持续交付的性能，其实战表现有待时间检验。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "甲骨文于上周发布全球最大云端 AI 超级计算机「OCI Zettascale10」，由 80 万块 NVIDIA GPU 组成，峰值算力高达 16 ZettaFLOPS，成为 OpenAI 「星际之门」集群的算力核心。",
    "甲骨文与 OpenAI 在德州阿比林（Abilene）共建了「星际之门」旗舰 AI 超级计算集群，而 OCI Zettascale10 正是其算力骨干。",
    "甲骨文研发的这套 RDMA over Converged Ethernet 网络（代号 Acceleron）将海量 GPU 紧密连接成一个整体，使得 OpenAI 的大模型训练能够在如此庞大的芯片阵列上高效运转。",
    "相比传统三级交换结构，Acceleron 减少了网络层级，使 GPU 对 GPU 的直连延迟更加一致，整体性能更具可预测性。",
    "甲骨文称这种创新网络既提高了效率又降低了成本，让客户可以用更少的电力完成同样的 AI 训练任务。",
    "然而，对于 16 ZFLOPS 的惊人算力，不少业内观察者持保留态度。该数据尚未经独立机构验证，而且很可能是基于理论峰值算力而非持续实效得出。"
  ],
